extend layout
block slide
  div(class='span12')
    div(id='myCarousel', class='carousel slide', data-ride='carousel')
      ol(class='carousel-indicators')
        li(data-slide-to='0', data-target='#myCarousel', class='active')
        li(data-slide-to='1', data-target='#myCarousel')
        li(data-slide-to='2', data-target='#myCarousel')
        li(data-slide-to='3', data-target='#myCarousel')
      div(class='carousel-inner')
        div(class='item active')
          img(src='img/1.jpg', alt='', style='width:100%;')
          div(class="carousel-caption")
            h3(style="color:black;") 
              | We provide business owners with analytical insights on local markets and customer experiences through integration of a variety of datasets including customer reviews, demographic and economic data.
            p
              form(method='get', action='/signup' class="form-inline")
                input(type='submit', value='Sign Up today!' class="btn btn-primary")
        div(class='item')
          img(src='img/2.jpg', alt='', style='width:100%;')
          div(class="carousel-caption")
            h3(style="color:white;")
              | We help restaurant owners better understand key drivers for customer behavior and satisfaction over time. It also benefits new business or established ones looking to expand in new locations on market analysis.
            p
              form(method='get', action='/signup' class="form-inline")
                input(type='submit', value='Sign Up today!' class="btn btn-primary")
        div(class='item')
          img(src='img/3.jpg', alt='', style='width:100%;')
          div(class="carousel-caption")
            h3(style="color:white;")
              | Business owners can navigate through factors impacting target markets, including local competitor landscape, income level, location preference, etc, and generate customized market analysis.
            p
              form(method='get', action='/signup' class="form-inline")
                input(type='submit', value='Sign Up today!' class="btn btn-primary")
        div(class='item')
          img(src='img/4.jpg', alt='', style='width:100%;')
          div(class="carousel-caption")
            h3(style="color:white;")
              | Our recommender system for customers can search businesses by various factors including location, category, distance, popularity and other attributes.
            p
              form(method='get', action='/signup' class="form-inline")
                input(type='submit', value='Sign Up today!' class="btn btn-primary")
        a(class='left carousel-control', data-slide='prev', href='#myCarousel')
            span(class='glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left') 
        a(class='right carousel-control', data-slide='next', href='#myCarousel')
            span(class='glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right')
block content
    h1(style="text-align:center;")
      | WELCOME
